description: DC's premier restaurant, Woodland's Vegan Bistro (formerly known as Everlasting Life Café, DC) is transforming their award winning cuisine into a masterful mobile operation full of unique & soulful plant based cuisine.  They are responding to the growing demand for cruelty - free options by the ever evolving conscious consumers of the surrounding cities, with plans to service the streets of DC, Maryland & VA.  Woodland's Vegan Bistro...To Go debuted their food truck on Saturday, August 3rd at the 2013 Mustock Festival in Lignum, VA, and have been going strong ever since. Stop by and see for yourself!
name: Woodlands Vegan Bistro
